data.description: Welcome to 2700 Monte Ranch Trail in distinguished Greatwood Estates! This 1.5 story home has been thoughtfully designed to capture luxurious living while maintaining practical functionality. Sitting on a corner lot with just over 1-acre and a fully fenced backyard, this stately home features striking curb appeal including uplights, a stone exterior and a Durango oversized iron front door. At almost 4,000 sq ft with 5 bedrooms, dedicated study, and 4 full baths, a stone entryway welcomes you into open concept living with notable fir cross beams, crown molding, high-end light fixtures, and gorgeous luxury 5” plank floors. The expansive horseshoe island with seating of up to 8 and stone-lined wall overlooks the living space with limestone fireplace and wood beam mantle creating an inviting atmosphere for all occasions. With meticulous attention to detail, the spacious kitchen with high-end fixtures and stainless steel appliances features double ovens, a myriad of cabinets with pull-outs, pendant lighting, gas cooktop, ample pantry space and a sizable dining area. The primary suite offers space, privacy and an exquisite spa-like bath. Three additional bedrooms and two bathrooms along with study are also on the first floor. Upstairs you’ll find a secondary living space, bedroom and full bathroom. Additional features include a French door with glass side panels in study, additional study nook, upgraded electrical options, recessed lighting, designer paint selection, exterior lights, full gutters, 500 gallon propane tank, and upgraded tile selections in the wet areas. An expanded covered patio providing outdoor living space that overlooks an expansive, fenced yard for limitless possibilities completes this must see home!
